  "2248270": {
    "name": "纸板 鱼",
    "steam_appid": 2248270,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248270/extras/150cc25f3b486dbb5228d136c83884b2.avif?t=1726880766\" width=609 height=140 /></span><br><br>一头扎进纸板鱼的迷人深处。沉浸在这款扣人心弦的第三人称游戏中，让您置身于势不可挡的英雄鱼 Nozzle 的鳍中。踏上一段迷人的旅程，穿越一个由物理学本身的线索错综复杂地编织而成的世界。准备好迎接一系列基于技能的互动和令人费解的谜题，保证取得进步和成就的令人心潮澎湃的时刻。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248270/extras/e044a99cb7f0421682d9d36066b44130.poster.avif?t=1726880766\" width=608 height=140 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248270/extras/e044a99cb7f0421682d9d36066b44130.webm?t=1726880766\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248270/extras/e044a99cb7f0421682d9d36066b44130.mp4?t=1726880766\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>当您踏入Nozzle 的水生鞋时，您将揭开纸板鱼现象的神秘起源。解开一个逐渐展开的故事，吸引你进入它的深度和阴谋。无缝应对一系列挑战，发挥你的足智多谋，解开那些敢于阻挡你前进道路的令人费解的谜团。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248270/extras/870f01e316217a1d1594b3444bfc7124.poster.avif?t=1726880766\" width=608 height=140 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248270/extras/870f01e316217a1d1594b3444bfc7124.webm?t=1726880766\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248270/extras/870f01e316217a1d1594b3444bfc7124.mp4?t=1726880766\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Nozzle 征服看似不可逾越的事物的神奇技巧将成为你的终极工具，为你面对逆境时的恢复能力铺平道路。无论事情变得多么艰难，利用诺兹坚定不移的决心和闪电般的智慧，你将引导他走向胜利和解放。即使是最艰巨的挑战也会在诺兹坚定的精神下崩溃，表明它们只不过是他通往荣耀之路的垫脚石。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248270/extras/d2fc1010207ebd898ecd2e69aa99f81b.poster.avif?t=1726880766\" width=608 height=140 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248270/extras/d2fc1010207ebd898ecd2e69aa99f81b.webm?t=1726880766\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248270/extras/d2fc1010207ebd898ecd2e69aa99f81b.mp4?t=1726880766\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>准备好一头扎进一个模糊现实与想象界限的领域。在好奇心、勇敢和征服未知世界的不屈动力的推动下，您将掌控缰绳，引导 Nozzle 经历一次难忘的冒险之旅。 《纸板鱼》邀请您成为 Nozzle 令人难以置信的故事中不可或缺的一部分，在这个故事中，创造性的解决方案克服了挑战，并从坚定的毅力中取得了胜利。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248270/extras/f30318466adc4b3d50de9117f95e3a0d.poster.avif?t=1726880766\" width=608 height=140 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248270/extras/f30318466adc4b3d50de9117f95e3a0d.webm?t=1726880766\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248270/extras/f30318466adc4b3d50de9117f95e3a0d.mp4?t=1726880766\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>抓住你的控制装置，让自己沉浸在这场非凡的冒险中。",
